                            <comment id="94824" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 24 Sep 2014 13:55:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Peter you can close this ticket as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3331&quot; title=&quot;Crash during mount/umount during stress testing&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3331&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3331&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. That work has landed which was similar to the work that came out of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4800&quot; title=&quot;no automatic module load in newer kernels&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4800&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4800&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="86813" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 17 Jun 2014 16:20:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Noticed several of the fixes done for this are also in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6420&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6420&lt;/a&gt;. for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3331&quot; title=&quot;Crash during mount/umount during stress testing&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3331&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3331&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. In the near future I will base my work on top of this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
